data.description: Come and see this two-story home that features a home office, formal, dining area, a spacious kitchen, tile flooring on the first floor, a game room, all bedrooms located upstairs, a cover patio, and a nice curb appeal. It's conveniently situated just a few miles away from The Woodlands Mall, with easy access to interstate 45 and the Hardy Toll Road.
